| image_caption  = Rabindranath Tagore in Kolkata, c. 1915
| date_of_birth  = [[7 May]] [[1861]]
| place_of_birth = [[Kolkata]], [[India]]
| date_of_death  = [[7 August]] [[1941]]
| place_of_death = [[Kolkata]], [[India]]
